Penggal kepala mereka!

44
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,079
Master Cho, kenapa kau kemari?

45
00:10:26,309 --> 00:10:29,079
Raja menyuruh kita memperketat
keamanan di malam hari.

46
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,120
<font color="#00ff00">CHO HWI RYANG, GURU PUTRA MAHKOTA</font>

47
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:33,289
Kita diminta untuk tak membiarkan
siapa pun memasuki benteng saat malam.

48
00:10:33,419 --> 00:10:35,490
Bagaimana kau tahu
cara membunuh mayat hidup?

49
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:38,559
Raja menyuruh kami
memenggal kepala mereka.

50
00:10:38,890 --> 00:10:41,329
