56
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:52,140
Kau mau ke mana selarut ini?

57
00:10:52,669 --> 00:10:55,980
Kurasa salah satu mayat hidup
memasuki benteng.

58
00:11:09,959 --> 00:11:11,020
Bagus.

